{"ID":"20260528162244-p7e7pne","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260528162244-p7e7pne","title":"2024年全国甲卷","type":"doc","updated":"20260619084540"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260528162244-hr3v9o8","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20260528162244-hr3v9o8","updated":"20260528162456"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"论述类文本"}]},{"ID":"20260528162416-tu3fb26","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162416-tu3fb26","updated":"20260528162416"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2019年4月23日，习近平主席在会见应邀出席中国人民解放军海军成立70周年多国海军活动的外方代表团团长时指出：“海洋对于人类社会生存和发展具有重要意义。海洋孕育了生命、联通了世界、促进了发展。我们人类居住的这个蓝色星球，不是被海洋分割成了各个孤岛，而是被海洋连结成了命运共同体，各国人民安危与共。”作为“人类命运共同体”的重要组成部分，海洋命运共同体的建设目标是打造一个持久和平、普遍安全、共同繁荣、开放包容、清洁美丽的海洋环境。"}]},{"ID":"20260528162416-bm2mnok","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162416-bm2mnok","updated":"20260528162416"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"要实现海洋的持久和平与普遍安全，各国必须摒弃传统的大国争霸思路，充分照顾彼此的安全关切和合理利益，联合起来打击海盗、人口走私、贩毒等海上犯罪行为，在涉及海洋权益争端时通过友好协商的方式来解决问题，短期内无法协商的问题可以考虑搁置争议。共同繁荣、开放包容和清洁美丽的愿景意味着，我们要坚持开放的自由贸易体系，同时共同应对气候变化、海洋环境保护等问题，发挥海洋作为国际贸易大通道的积极作用，关注发展中国家的发展诉求。随着人类技术水平的提升和各国经济发展对资源需求的日益增加，各国都希望开发利用更多的海洋资源。如何才能在更好地利用海洋资源的同时又促进可持续发展、构建海洋命运共同体？习近平总书记提出海洋发展的“四个转变”：“要提高海洋资源开发能力，着力推动海洋经济向质量效益型转变”；“要保护海洋生态环境，着力推动海洋开发方式向循环利用型转变”；“要发展海洋科学技术，着力推动海洋科技向创新引领型转变”；“要维护国家海洋权益，着力推动海洋维权向统筹兼顾型转变”。这为海洋开发利用指明了方向。"}]},{"ID":"20260528162416-i7uegbo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162416-i7uegbo","updated":"20260528162416"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"具体到全球、地区和双边层面，构建海洋命运共同体应该着眼于不同的路径，这样才更具有可行性。"}]},{"ID":"20260528162416-82mmu2g","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162416-82mmu2g","updated":"20260528162416"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在全球层面，构建海洋命运共同体主要着眼于涉海全球公共问题的治理，各国应致力于构建更加公正合理、稳定有效的国际法和国际规则体系。目前，发达国家和发展中国家在海洋资源的开发利用方面仍然存在矛盾。发达国家过于强调公海自由原则，希望利用技术上的优势开发更多的公海资源。发展中国家更多强调公海作为人类共同财产的原则。如果公海被确定为人类共同财产，那么它就不得被占有，所有国家共同参加公海管理，积极分享公海开发中获取的利益，并保障公海只用于和平目的。人类共同财产原则更有利于保护公海环境和对海洋资源的可持续开发利用，对于实现持久和平与共同繁荣的愿景来说更为可行。总的来说，全球层面的海洋命运共同体构建，应着眼于建立更加有效的合作制度体系。"}]},{"ID":"20260528162416-ll1ht8m","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162416-ll1ht8m","updated":"20260528162416"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在地区和双边层面，由于相关成员在海洋利益方面拥有更多的交集，海洋命运共同体的构建应着眼于以下几个方面：其一，如果某个地区内或者两国间存在海洋权益争端，应该致力于让局势降温，避免引发军事冲突，为海上贸易和人员往来提供安全的环境。地区大国和地区性的安全架构应该在这一方面发挥主要作用。其二，建立高水平的区域经济合作制度，充分发挥海洋作为运输大动脉的作用，提升两国间或者地区内成员国之间的经济交流水平。其三，对两国或者本地区的海洋环境保护开展联合行动，保护海洋资源、打击海上违法犯罪以及联合进行海上搜救等。"}]},{"ID":"20260528162416-k8s2xiz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162416-k8s2xiz","updated":"20260528162416"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（摘编自宋伟《海洋命运共同体构建与新的海洋文明》）"}]},{"ID":"20260528162244-0ptdeme","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260528162244-0ptdeme","updated":"20260528162456"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"题目"}]},{"ID":"20260528162456-t357kyz","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260528162456-t357kyz","updated":"20260528162456"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260528162456-r2n3hyl","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260528162456-r2n3hyl","updated":"20260528162456"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260528162456-ajxc41k","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162456-ajxc41k","updated":"20260528162456"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"下列关于原文内容的理解和分析，不正确的一项是（   ）"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260528162456-d4scqsc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162456-d4scqsc","updated":"20260528162456"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A. 各国之间可能存在或大或小的海洋权益争端，但这不应妨碍争议各方携手参与海洋命运共同体的构建。"}]},{"ID":"20260528162456-a8npvbl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162456-a8npvbl","updated":"20260528162456"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B. 如何在保障人类更好利用海洋资源"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Properties":{"style":"width: 14px;"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"data:image/wmf;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAA4AAAATAQMAAACazq7XAAAAAXNSR0ICQMB9xQAAAAZQTFRFAAAAAAAApWe5zwAAAAF0Uk5TAEDm2GYAAAAJcEhZcwAADsQAAA7EAZUrDhsAAAAZdEVYdFNvZnR3YXJlAE1pY3Jvc29mdCBPZmZpY2V/7TVxAAAAK0lEQVQY02NgAAMOBxASqGGwa2FQZmFQAiIXBjsVBiUVMBuM7ICkBAMMAACJWwQoAyaijwAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=="},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"width: 14px;\"}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"同时促进可持续发展，这是构建海洋命运共同体需要应对的挑战。"}]},{"ID":"20260528162456-oxrxzk2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162456-oxrxzk2","updated":"20260528162456"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C. 在全球层面，既有的国际法和国际规则体系不够完备，效率不高，也没有建立起相应的合作制度体系。"}]},{"ID":"20260528162456-zm7e0y1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162456-zm7e0y1","updated":"20260528162456"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D. 高水平的区域经济合作制度，有利于发挥海运优势，促进经济交流，是构建海洋命运共同体的一部分。"}]},{"ID":"20260528162456-p3bblec","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260528162456-p3bblec","updated":"20260528162456"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260528162456-ckajucc","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20260528162456-ckajucc","updated":"20260528162456"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260528162456-s6mysuk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162456-s6mysuk","updated":"20260528162456"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"下列对原文论证的相关分析，正确的一项是（   ）"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260528162456-16oq7al","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162456-16oq7al","updated":"20260528162456"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A. 文章着眼于人类社会生存和发展，主要论述了海洋命运共同体的建设目标和愿景。"}]},{"ID":"20260528162456-xf6so9t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162456-xf6so9t","updated":"20260528162456"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B. 文章用了较大篇幅讨论海洋的发展和生态环保问题，凸显了这些问题的优先性。"}]},{"ID":"20260528162456-fhceqkq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162456-fhceqkq","updated":"20260528162456"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C. 第四段对比发达国家和发展中国家的不同主张，以证明公海是人类的共同财产。"}]},{"ID":"20260528162456-vsu0t6y","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162456-vsu0t6y","updated":"20260528162456"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D. 文章围绕海洋命运共同体的理念展开，分析问题时注意区分不同的角度和层次。"}]},{"ID":"20260528162456-zcmdy4w","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260528162456-zcmdy4w","updated":"20260528162456"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260528162456-dx8ncei","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"My4=","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20260528162456-dx8ncei","updated":"20260528162456"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260528162456-0yh60te","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162456-0yh60te","updated":"20260528162456"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"根据原文内容，下列说法不正确的一项是（   ）"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260528162456-vxib67h","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162456-vxib67h","updated":"20260528162456"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A. 传统的大国争霸思路更多关注本国利益，容易引发海洋地缘纷争，威胁海洋安全。"}]},{"ID":"20260528162456-otk83cy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162456-otk83cy","updated":"20260528162456"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B. 构建海洋命运共同体，应当从地区和双边逐步推广至全球，这样才更有可行性。"}]},{"ID":"20260528162456-dkpix9j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162456-dkpix9j","updated":"20260528162456"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C. 人类共同财产的原则并不反对公海资源开发，也不谋求任何国家权益的优先性。"}]},{"ID":"20260528162456-vvxx0he","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162456-vvxx0he","updated":"20260528162456"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D. 在海洋命运共同体的构建中，地区大国和地区性的安全架构理应发挥更大的作用。"}]},{"ID":"20260528162244-p45yjtm","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260528162244-p45yjtm","updated":"20260528162632"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"答案"}]},{"ID":"20260528162523-finu06r","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260528162523-finu06r","updated":"20260528162600"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260528162523-nv9sho7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260528162523-nv9sho7","updated":"20260528162523"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260528162523-4uya2yx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162523-4uya2yx","updated":"20260528162542"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C    2. D    3. B"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260528162632-0w187yi","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260528162632-0w187yi","updated":"20260528162743"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"解析"}]},{"ID":"20260528162712-fz35idq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162712-fz35idq","updated":"20260528162712"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"【1题详解】"}]},{"ID":"20260528162712-w2u29sm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162712-w2u29sm","updated":"20260528162712"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"本题考查学生对原文内容"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Properties":{"style":"width: 14px;"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"data:image/wmf;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAA4AAAATAQMAAACazq7XAAAAAXNSR0ICQMB9xQAAAAZQTFRFAAAAAAAApWe5zwAAAAF0Uk5TAEDm2GYAAAAJcEhZcwAADsQAAA7EAZUrDhsAAAAZdEVYdFNvZnR3YXJlAE1pY3Jvc29mdCBPZmZpY2V/7TVxAAAAK0lEQVQY02NgAAMOBxASqGGwa2FQZmFQAiIXBjsVBiUVMBuM7ICkBAMMAACJWwQoAyaijwAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=="},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"width: 14px;\"}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"理解和分析能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260528162712-ygq6rx6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162712-ygq6rx6","updated":"20260528162712"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C.“既有的国际法和国际规则体系不够完备，效率不高，也没有建立起相应的合作制度体系”错误。原文提到的是“在全球层面，构建海洋命运共同体主要着眼于涉海全球公共问题的治理，各国应致力于构建更加公正合理、稳定有效的国际法和国际规则体系”“总的来说，全球层面的海洋命运共同体构建，应着眼于建立更加有效的合作制度体系”，可见并没有说现有的体系不够完备，效率不高，也没有提到没有建立起相应的合作制度体系，只是强调要“更加公正合理、稳定有效”“更加有效”，选项曲解文意，无中生有。"}]},{"ID":"20260528162712-ggt5uu0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162712-ggt5uu0","updated":"20260528162712"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选C。"}]},{"ID":"20260528162712-2norir1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162712-2norir1","updated":"20260528162712"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"【2题详解】"}]},{"ID":"20260528162712-cghzy21","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162712-cghzy21","updated":"20260528162712"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"本题考查学生对原文论证的相关分析能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260528162712-d4zk8ks","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162712-d4zk8ks","updated":"20260528162712"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A.“主要论述了海洋命运共同体的建设目标和愿景”错误。文章开头先说明了海洋的重要性，进而提出海洋命运共同体的建设目标，而正文主体部分主要论证的是如何实现目标，也就是构建海洋命运共同体的着眼点，即怎么做的问题，可见主要论述的并非海洋命运共同体的建设目标和愿景。"}]},{"ID":"20260528162712-hxprq9p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162712-hxprq9p","updated":"20260528162712"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B.“凸显了这些问题的优先性”错误。选项中的“这些”指“海洋的发展和生态环保问题”，讨论的目的在于引出解决问题的方法，即“如何才能在更好地利用海洋资源的同时又促进可持续发展、构建海洋命运共同体？”可见并非“凸显了这些问题的优先性”，理解偏颇，曲解文意。"}]},{"ID":"20260528162712-py62ke5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162712-py62ke5","updated":"20260528162712"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C.“以证明公海是人类的共同财产”错误。第四段对比发达国家和发展中国家的不同主张，是为了得出“人类共同财产原则更有利于保护公海环境和对海洋资源的可持续开发利用，对于实现持久和平与共同繁荣的愿景来说更为可行”，进而归结到：全球层面的海洋命运共同体构建，应着眼于建立更加有效的合作制度体系。"}]},{"ID":"20260528162712-rhawy48","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162712-rhawy48","updated":"20260528162712"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选D。"}]},{"ID":"20260528162712-nqj7dt9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162712-nqj7dt9","updated":"20260528162712"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"【3题详解】"}]},{"ID":"20260528162712-gyg9a14","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162712-gyg9a14","updated":"20260528162712"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"本题考查学生理解作者观点态度并进行合理推断的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260528162712-y5dxhw6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162712-y5dxhw6","updated":"20260528162712"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B.“应当从地区和双边逐步推广至全球，这样才更有可行性”错误。倒数第三段说“具体到全球、地区和双边层面，构建海洋命运共同体应该着眼于不同的路径，这样才更具有可行性”，选项偷换信息，“这样”指代对象不同，文中可行性的内容并非“从地区和双边逐步推广至全球”，且结合后数三段分析“全球层面”“地区和双边层面”为平行并列关系，而不是“从地区和双边逐步推广至全球”，选项曲解文意。"}]},{"ID":"20260528162712-o6hdka7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162712-o6hdka7","updated":"20260528162712"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选B。"}]},{"ID":"20260528162744-82wnn5z","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20260528162744-82wnn5z","updated":"20260619084540"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"实用类文本"}]},{"ID":"20260528162806-uwonzka","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162806-uwonzka","updated":"20260528162806"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"“偷梁换柱”多指以假代真，用欺骗的手段改变事物的性质，然而在古建筑工程领域，“偷梁换柱”却属于一种科学实用的修缮加固方法。"}]},{"ID":"20260528162806-fs14hrw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162806-fs14hrw","updated":"20260528162806"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"梁是截面形状一般为长方形的木料，且木料的长度尺寸远大于截面尺寸。梁为水平放置，两端的底部有支撑构件。梁主要用于承担建筑上部构件及屋顶的全部重量，并把这些重量向下传给支撑构件。柱为梁的支撑构件。柱子截面形状一般为圆形，长度尺寸远大于截面直径。柱子为竖向放置，主要用于承担上部梁传来的重量，并向下传递给下部的梁或直接传至地面。梁与柱采用榫卯形式连接，形成稳固的大木结构体系。位于屋架内的若干梁在竖向被层层往上“抬”，上下梁之间由短柱支撑，底部的梁由立于地面的立柱支撑。梁、柱均为中国木结构古建筑的核心受力、传力构件，缺一不可。"}]},{"ID":"20260528162806-lo9hkub","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162806-lo9hkub","updated":"20260528162806"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"对于古建筑而言，立于地面的立柱，或因长期承受上部结构传来的重量而产生开裂残损，或因柱底部位长期受到地面潮气影响而出现糟朽残损，这导致木柱强度下降，无法正常支撑梁。此时可采用“偷梁换柱”的加固方法。“偷梁换柱”实际就是“托梁换柱”。其基本做法为：首先将“假柱”（即临时的竖向支撑构件）安装在梁底部、原柱（原有立柱）旁边；再抽去原柱，使梁传来的重量暂时由“假柱”承担；然后安装新柱，新柱的材料、尺寸及安装位置与原有立柱相同；最后将“假柱”移去。"}]},{"ID":"20260528162806-nrwi8d6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162806-nrwi8d6","updated":"20260528162806"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"完善的“偷梁换柱”加固方法具有科学性，其原理主要包括三个方面：其一，从梁的角度而言，它是水平受力构件，并把外力向下传给立柱。梁只有保持水平稳定状态，才能保证整个大木结构的稳定。在加固古建筑的过程中，梁始终受到支托，因而能一直保持水平稳定状态。其二，从柱的角度而言，它是竖向支撑构件，并最终把上部构件的重量传给地基。只有立柱具有充足的承载力，且与梁有可靠连接时，才能有效承担梁传来的作用力。加固过程中，技术人员虽然将原柱抽去，但是预先将“假柱”设置于原柱附近，让“假柱”代替原柱发挥支撑作用，因而换柱过程对结构整体的稳定基本无影响。换柱完成后，新柱与原柱有着同样的材料、尺寸，且与梁有着相同的可靠连接方式，它完全能够代替原柱发挥支撑作用。其三，从梁、柱整体结构角度而言，“偷梁换柱”方法对整体结构干扰小，且能达到良好的加固效果：原柱被新柱原位替换，新柱不仅有很好的支撑作用，而且与梁仍有可靠连接；“假柱”仅用于加固过程的临时支撑，且在原柱撤去后新柱安装前，能够与梁临时组成稳定的结构体系。因此，在“偷梁换柱”过程中，梁、柱结构整体始终处于稳定状态。"}]},{"ID":"20260528162806-2daqoi6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162806-2daqoi6","updated":"20260619084540"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Properties":{"style":"width: 521px;"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"学科网(www.zxxk.com)--教育资源门户，提供试卷、教案、课件、论文、素材以及各类教学资源下载，还有大量而丰富的教学相关资讯！"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/学科网www.zxxk.com--教育资源门户，提供试卷、教案、课件、论文、素材以及各类教学资源下载，还有大量而丰富的教学相关资讯！-20260528162806-069plal.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"width: 521px;\"}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]},{"ID":"20260528162806-uw10766","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162806-uw10766","updated":"20260528162806"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"中国古建筑大木构架剖面示意图"}]},{"ID":"20260528162806-k3is834","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162806-k3is834","updated":"20260528162806"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（摘编自周乾《故宫建筑细探》）"}]},{"ID":"20260528162828-p0nqjni","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260528162828-p0nqjni","updated":"20260528162842"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"题目"}]},{"ID":"20260528162842-xdqmmyh","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260528162842-xdqmmyh","updated":"20260528162842"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260528162842-xcxqh98","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"NC4=","Num":4},"Properties":{"id":"20260528162842-xcxqh98","updated":"20260528162842"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260528162842-k1mxeay","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162842-k1mxeay","updated":"20260528162842"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"下列对原文相关内容的理解和分析，不正确的一项是（  ）"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260528162842-t5w3e7u","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162842-t5w3e7u","updated":"20260528162842"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A. “偷梁换柱”这一成语在现今的使用中多含有贬义的色彩，但在古建筑工程领域，它是指一种修缮加固的科学方法，完全没有贬义。"}]},{"ID":"20260528162842-wfysxwc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162842-wfysxwc","updated":"20260528162842"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B. 中国古建筑大木构架剖面示意图展示了几种不同位置、不同尺寸的柱，这些柱子中，立于地面的立柱比较容易发生糟朽残损的情况。"}]},{"ID":"20260528162842-u07ikuf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162842-u07ikuf","updated":"20260528162842"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C. 结合图文可以发现，屋顶的重量由上层柱承担，然后传给梁，再由梁传递给其下的短柱，依次向下传递，最终由底部的立柱传至地面。"}]},{"ID":"20260528162842-clulcpg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162842-clulcpg","updated":"20260528162842"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D. “偷梁换柱”的加固方法包括托梁、抽柱、换柱等步骤，在每一个步骤中梁一直会得到很好的支撑，从而始终能够保持水平稳定状态。"}]},{"ID":"20260528162842-cwqnuhc","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260528162842-cwqnuhc","updated":"20260528162842"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260528162842-mxqtm3q","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"NS4=","Num":5},"Properties":{"id":"20260528162842-mxqtm3q","updated":"20260528162842"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260528162842-zwycvy5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162842-zwycvy5","updated":"20260528162842"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"请根据原文内容，在下面文段的横线处补写出恰当的词语。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260528162842-yhgfhfk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162842-yhgfhfk","updated":"20260528162842"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"工程实例：故宫太和殿是我国最大的木构大殿，明清两代帝王即位或节日庆典都在此举行。2004年，技术人员在对太和殿进行勘查时，发现有一根立柱下部三分之一的位置出现了严重糟朽，于是采取了“偷梁换柱”的方法对该立柱进行加固。具体过程如下：先使用“假柱”托住原柱上部的梁。“假柱”为完好的木料，被安装在"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"附近，用于临时支撑梁。再把柱子底部糟朽部分抽去，以便用"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"代替。原柱糟朽部分去掉后，剩余的部分做成巴掌形，与新柱搭接。新柱与被抽去的糟朽部分同材料、同形状、同尺寸，且顶部亦做成巴掌榫形状。最后再把"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"拆除，即完成了原有立柱的加固。"}]},{"ID":"20260528162842-9tzzue9","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260528162842-9tzzue9","updated":"20260528162842"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260528162842-ellkkhe","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"Ni4=","Num":6},"Properties":{"id":"20260528162842-ellkkhe","updated":"20260528162842"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260528162842-vlwnrwl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162842-vlwnrwl","updated":"20260528162849"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"清代的古籍中有另一种“偷梁换柱”的记载：当某根立柱损坏需要更换时，为节省工料，工匠只是在原柱旁边设一根新柱再撤去原柱。为什么第2题“工程实例”中，太和殿修缮没有采用这种更简便的加固方式呢？请简要分析。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260528162903-1c2rjvm","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260528162903-1c2rjvm","updated":"20260528162922"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"答案"}]},{"ID":"20260528162921-astl5lx","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260528162921-astl5lx","updated":"20260528162921"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260528162921-rzvyeiw","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"NC4=","Num":4},"Properties":{"id":"20260528162921-rzvyeiw","updated":"20260528162921"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260528162921-mkox1k2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162921-mkox1k2","updated":"20260528162921"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C    5.     ①. 原柱    ②. 新柱    ③. 假柱"}]}]},{"ID":"20260528162921-64g9l4u","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"NS4=","Num":5},"Properties":{"id":"20260528162921-64g9l4u","updated":"20260528162921"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260528162921-r4h9d4v","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162921-r4h9d4v","updated":"20260528162921"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"①新柱如果没有原位替换原柱，可能会改变建筑原结构的受力和传力方式，影响整体的稳定性；"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260528162921-34p7tpw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162921-34p7tpw","updated":"20260528162921"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"②太和殿是中国最大的木构大殿，建造之初工匠们应该经过了精心的测量，原位替换才是最佳的解决方案；"}]},{"ID":"20260528162921-hqvlf0y","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162921-hqvlf0y","updated":"20260528162921"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"③太和殿的修缮加固追求最大程度地保持文物原貌，节省工料不是优先考虑的因素。"}]},{"ID":"20260528162922-i13nzwu","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260528162922-i13nzwu","updated":"20260528162940"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"解析"}]},{"ID":"20260528162940-3vvaur4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162940-3vvaur4","updated":"20260528162940"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"【4题详解】"}]},{"ID":"20260528162940-0iztwfd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162940-0iztwfd","updated":"20260528162940"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"本题考查学生理解、分析文章内容和理解图表的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260528162940-ahrl5bg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162940-ahrl5bg","updated":"20260528162940"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C.“屋顶"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Properties":{"style":"width: 14px;"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"data:image/wmf;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAA4AAAATAQMAAACazq7XAAAAAXNSR0ICQMB9xQAAAAZQTFRFAAAAAAAApWe5zwAAAAF0Uk5TAEDm2GYAAAAJcEhZcwAADsQAAA7EAZUrDhsAAAAZdEVYdFNvZnR3YXJlAE1pY3Jvc29mdCBPZmZpY2V/7TVxAAAAK0lEQVQY02NgAAMOBxASqGGwa2FQZmFQAiIXBjsVBiUVMBuM7ICkBAMMAACJWwQoAyaijwAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=="},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"width: 14px;\"}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"重量由上层柱承担，然后传给梁”错误，原文第二段“梁为水平放置”“梁主要用于承担建筑上部构件及屋顶的全部重量，并把这些重量向下传给支撑构件”，示意图中线条指示的横着的木料是“梁”，它承担屋顶的全部重量。选项受力、传力分析不对。"}]},{"ID":"20260528162940-n8aj57j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162940-n8aj57j","updated":"20260528162940"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选C。"}]},{"ID":"20260528162940-dpks3y8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162940-dpks3y8","updated":"20260528162940"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"【5题详解】"}]},{"ID":"20260528162940-lexw1ii","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162940-lexw1ii","updated":"20260528162940"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"本题考查学生筛选整合信息、根据文本信息进行判断推理和情境补写的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260528162940-s7watg7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162940-s7watg7","updated":"20260528162940"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"试题以故宫太和殿的修缮工程实例为题面，要求学生在理解“偷梁换柱”全过程，尤其是原柱、“假柱”、新柱三者关系的基础上，补写空缺内容。"}]},{"ID":"20260528162940-i7jvazm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162940-i7jvazm","updated":"20260528162940"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"题干中“具体过程如下”可对应材料第三段的“其基本做法为……”。"}]},{"ID":"20260528162940-qeed48m","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162940-qeed48m","updated":"20260528162940"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"第①处，“被安装在……附近”，对应材料的“首先将‘假柱’（即临时的竖向支撑构件）安装在梁底部、原柱（原有立柱）旁边”或第四段“预先将‘假柱’设置于原柱附近”，“附近”与“旁边”意思相近，故填“原柱”。"}]},{"ID":"20260528162940-31bn4d3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162940-31bn4d3","updated":"20260528162940"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"第②处，“以便用……代替”，对应“使梁传来的重量暂时由‘假柱’承担；然后安装新柱，新柱的材料、尺寸及安装位置与原有立柱相同”或第四段“原柱被新柱原位替换”，“假柱”只是代替原柱发挥支撑作用，真正用于替换的应该是“新柱”，故填“新柱”。"}]},{"ID":"20260528162940-v5o8ama","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162940-v5o8ama","updated":"20260528162940"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"第③处，“最后再把……拆除”，对应“最后将‘假柱’移去”，“假柱”的引号不能删除，因为表示特定称谓，故填“‘假柱’”。"}]},{"ID":"20260528162940-s44ljvp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162940-s44ljvp","updated":"20260528162940"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"【6题详解】"}]},{"ID":"20260528162940-60vgg41","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162940-60vgg41","updated":"20260528162940"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"本题考查学生筛选并整合信息、根据文本信息进行判断推理的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260528162940-cgpyslg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162940-cgpyslg","updated":"20260528162940"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"题干中的方法“更简便”，但是由材料和上一题的信息可知：完善的“偷梁换柱”加固方法具有科学性。"}]},{"ID":"20260528162940-pbsltes","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162940-pbsltes","updated":"20260528162940"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"首先，从受力分析角度看，原文第四段从三个角度“从梁的角度而言……保证整个大木结构的稳定”“从柱的角度而言……对结构整体的稳定基本无影响”“从梁、柱整体结构角度而言……组成稳定的结构体系”，进行受力、传力分析，得出：原位替换可以保证整体的稳定性。"}]},{"ID":"20260528162940-n6vp2py","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162940-n6vp2py","updated":"20260528162940"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"其次，从工匠精神的“精益求精”追求看，上一题的材料中指出“故宫太和殿是我国最大的木构大殿，明清两代帝王即位或节日庆典都在此举行”，大殿设计、建造之初，必定组织大量能工巧匠进行了精心的设计、测量等工作，原位替换更符合整体设计，因而是最佳修缮方案。"}]},{"ID":"20260528162940-qoiqkj2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162940-qoiqkj2","updated":"20260528162940"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"最后，从修缮原则、文物保护角度看，“修旧如故”，不追求节省工料，而应尽可能地保持其原有"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Properties":{"style":"width: 14px;"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"data:image/wmf;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAA4AAAATAQMAAACazq7XAAAAAXNSR0ICQMB9xQAAAAZQTFRFAAAAAAAApWe5zwAAAAF0Uk5TAEDm2GYAAAAJcEhZcwAADsQAAA7EAZUrDhsAAAAZdEVYdFNvZnR3YXJlAE1pY3Jvc29mdCBPZmZpY2V/7TVxAAAAK0lEQVQY02NgAAMOBxASqGGwa2FQZmFQAiIXBjsVBiUVMBuM7ICkBAMMAACJWwQoAyaijwAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=="},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"width: 14px;\"}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"历史形态和特征，以尊重和保护其历史价值和文化意义。上一题的材料中，在修缮时将“原柱糟朽部分去掉后，剩余的部分做成巴掌形，与新柱搭接。新柱与被抽去的糟朽部分同材料、同形状、同尺寸，且顶部亦做成巴掌榫形状”，这样能够最大程度地保持文物原貌，"}]},{"ID":"20260528162940-jdbtf8c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260528162940-jdbtf8c","updated":"20260528162940"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"该题不要求学生作答面面俱到，只要回答出两点即可。如果有其他的答案，言之成理亦可。"}]}]}